title: Static Analysis

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION.description: Access fine location sources, such as the Global Positioning System on the phone, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine where you are and may consume additional battery power.

android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATIO.description: Access coarse location sources, such as the mobile network database, to determine an approximate phone location, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine approximately where you are.

android.permission.CALL_PHONE.description: Allows the application to call phone numbers without your intervention. Malicious applications may cause unexpected calls on your phone bill. Note that this does not allow the application to call emergency numbers.

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.READ_CONTACTS.description: Allows an application to read all of the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to send your data to other people.

android.permission.WRITE_CONTACTS.description: Allows an application to modify the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to erase or modify your contact data.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS.description: Allows application to modify global audio settings, such as volume and routing.

android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to access the list of accounts known by the phone.

android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO.description: Allows application to access the audio record path.

android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to connect to and disconnect from Wi-Fi access points and to make changes to configured Wi-Fi networks.

android.permission.GET_TASKS.description: Allows application to retrieve information about currently and recently running tasks. May allow malicious applications to discover private information about other applications.

android.permission.DISABLE_KEYGUARD.description: Allows an application to disable the key lock and any associated password security. A legitimate example of this is the phone disabling the key lock when receiving an incoming phone call, then re-enabling the key lock when the call is finished.

android.permission.BLUETOOTH.description: Allows an application to view configuration of the local Bluetooth phone and to make and accept connections with paired devices.

com.android.launcher.permission.INSTALL_.description: Allows an application to install a shortcut in Launcher.

com.android.launcher.permission.UNINSTAL.description: Don't use this permission in your app. This permission is no longer supported.

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from SD Card.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

com.google.android.gms.permission.ACTIVI.info: allow application to recognize physical activity
com.google.android.gms.permission.ACTIVI.description: Allows an application to recognize physical activity.

manifest_analysis.title:
Clear text traffic is Enabled For App
[android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.
manifest_analysis.name: Clear text traffic is Enabled For App [android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]

strings: "Key_5001_call_poor_network_tips_content" : "Your device has a bad network connection. You may experience poor call quality."
"Key_5017_received_push_sent_tips_1" : "A read alert has been sent to %s.Do you want to"
"Key_5019_received_push_sent_tips_3" : "Note: If the sender is not on Kiki, a read alert is sent when you read a message."
"Key_5022_show_unread_out" : "While browsing unread messages, you cannot save, delete, or send messages."

"Key_5029_purchase_call_plan_notes" : "1. Once the calling package expires, the phone number will also expire. The remaining texts and voice minutes will be voided too.
2. Sending and receiving texts are counted separately.
3. Calls and texts only apply to US, Canada, Mexico and China, while you can receive calls and texts from any countries."

"Key_5029_purchase_call_plan_notes_multicountry" : "1. Once the calling package expires, the phone number will also expire. The remaining texts and voice minutes will be voided too.
2. Sending and receiving texts are counted separately.
3. Calls and texts only apply to %s, while you can receive calls and texts from any countries."

"Key_5037_call_forwarding_notes" : "Forwarding incoming calls to another phone number (Limited to US, Canada ,Mexico and China phone numbers). 
Note: Call forwarding uses double voice minutes."
"Key_5039_refill_notes" : "The new expiration date is determined by the remaining time in the current package and the length of the new package."
"Key_5040_refill_old_plan" : "The Small Package is no longer available to purchase new but you can still renew a previously-purchased Small Package."

"Key_5041_refill_recommend_notes" : "Large Text Package is recommended 
based on your past usage."
"Key_5050_read_alert_introduction_content" : "If you are not on Kiki when the recipient reads your messages, you will receive an alert. This can help you connect with the recipient quickly."
"Key_5057_useless_email" : "It's not the Email associated with your Kiki ID. If you want to use other Kiki account to login, please delete and reinstall your Kiki App."

"Key_5058_feedback_self_destruct_message" : "Self-destruct messaging requires both the sender and recipient have the Kiki app. Messages sent from your Kiki phone numbers to non-Kiki contacts cannot be self-destructed or recalled."

"Key_5059_tips_SMS_pic_content_1" : "Your messaging security setting does not change how messages you received are self-destructed. It is always the sender who controls how messages are self-destructed"

"Key_5064_feedback_help_restore" : "To ensure maximum security, Kiki is designed to run on one device.

Please read the following instructions carefully if you need to use Kiki on a new device.

1. Create a master password on this device.

2. Install Kiki on the new device then choose "Restore" and enter the master password.

3. You will no longer be able to use Kiki on this device as soon as you log in to Kiki on the new device.

Note: Your photos, videos, and other content protected by Kiki cannot be moved from one device to another."

"Key_5077_tips_email_alarm_content_1" : "When someone (including you) tries to log in to Kiki with the wrong password, Kiki will take a picture from the front camera and record the location. You can view the intruder login history here."

"Key_5078_tips_email_alarm_content_2" : "You can also enter an Email address to receive intrusion alarms. This is a very useful feature if you lose your phone or leave it unattended.
Set up Email Alarm NOW."
"Key_5079_tips_email_alarm_link_2" : "You can view the intruder login history here."
"Key_5080_number_name_empty" : "You must enter a name for the phone number."
"Key_5081_record_your_greeting_warning_content" : "Would you like to record and save a greeting now?"
"Key_5090_15m_wait" : "It takes about %1$d minutes to activate the phone number. Please wait %2$d minutes before making a call."

"Key_5092_incorrect_master_password_email_2" : "Hi,

Someone tried to login Kiki on your device（%1$s）with an incorrect master password:
Time: %2$s
Location: %3$s
Photo of the intruder: Please view the attached picture.
Password: %4$s

Thanks for using Kiki,
Kiki Service"
"Key_5100_please_set_master_password_warning" : "Please set up account recover information first!"
"Key_5102_master_password_login_box_warning_1_content" : "Please enter the master password (not your Kiki password). You can still try %s times."
"Key_5103_master_password_login_box_warning_2_content" : "Forgot password? You can still try %s times. You can also reset the master password with the security information you set up."
"Key_5112_account_recover_warning_1" : "Please enter a valid Email address first!"
"Key_5120_destroy_account_note" : "All your personal information and content in Kiki will be permanently deleted once you deactivate your account."
"Key_5122_delete_decoy_note" : "When you delete this password, all the information (messages, photos, videos, etc.) protected by the password will also be permanently deleted."

"Key_5129_set_email_enter_note" : "This Email address will be used to:
1. Receive intrusion alarms if someone tries to access Kiki.
2. Restore Kiki on a new device.
3. Reset the master password."
"Key_5132_set_email_confirm_note_2" : "To confirm your Email address, please click the link in the confirmation Email we sent you."
"Key_5133_set_email_confirm_note_3" : "Tap "OK" after you confirm your Email address."
"Key_5138_set_email_confirm_warning_1" : "The previous confirmation Email will be canceled."
"Key_5139_set_email_confirm_warning_content" : "You did not confirm your Email address by clicking the link embedded in the confirmation Email."
"Key_5145_set_email_success_set_master_password_note" : "Reset your Kiki password or log in to Kiki on a new device."
"Key_5149_set_master_password_introduce_title" : "Why do you need the master password?"
"Key_5150_set_master_password_introduce_1" : "1. Without the master password, you cannot rescure your account if you forget Kiki password."
"Key_5151_set_master_password_introduce_2" : "2. You need the master password to log in to your Kiki account on a new device."
"Key_5152_set_master_password_introduce_3" : "3. The master password can be used to reset the dot-lock for the Kiki vault."
"Key_5154_set_master_password_1_note" : "Use at least 8 characters. Must include letters in mixed case and numbers."
"Key_5157_set_master_password_1_warning_1_content" : "A password is required to protect your privacy. Please enter 4-16 numbers as your password."
"Key_5160_security_question_note" : "A secret question & answer can be used to reset the master password."
"Key_5168_security_fences_warning_1" : "Please enter a name for the Geo Fence."
"Key_5170_set_master_password_done" : "You have successfully set up the master password."
"Key_5171_destroy_account_confirm_note" : "All your personal information and content (contacts, photos, videos, notes and message history) will be permanently deleted."

"Key_5178_delete_decoy_confirm_warning" : "Are you sure you want to delete the decoy password?
All your personal information and content (contacts, photos, videos, notes and message history) protected by this password will be permanently deleted."

"Key_5184_intro_master_password_content" : "Please set up the master password that can be used to reset your Kiki password if you forget it. 
The master password is also the only way to log"
"Key_5187_intro_master_password_warning" : "You can also set up account recover information from "More"->"My Account"."

"feedback_help_calling_plan" : "1. Each calling package has an expiration date. Please renew or refill the calling package before it expires.

2. If your calling package has already expired, you have also lost your Kiki phone number. We cannot help you on this issue.

3. In rare situations, the phone number you chose right before purchasing the calling package may become unavailable. Don't worry, we don't just grab your money and run. You can select another phone number for the calling package you already purchased.

4. We do not automatically renew your calling package. There is no recurring charge.

If the above answers do not address your question, please contact us."

"feedback_help_coverme_phone_number" : "2. We only provide U.S. and Canadian phone numbers at this time and you can only make calls and send texts to U.S., Canadian, and Chinese phone numbers. However, you can receive calls and texts from any phone number anywhere in the world.

U.K. phone numbers coming soon!

3. A Kiki phone number is always attached to a calling package you have purchased. If the calling package expires, you permanently lose the phone number. Please make sure you renew your calling package before it expires.

4. You can get up to 10 Kiki phone numbers simultaneously.

5. We always recommend that you invite your contacts to use the Kiki app too. Calling and texting between Kiki users is more secure and is always free.

If the above answers do not address your question, please contact us."
"feedback_help_export_conversation_history" : "Kiki is designed to protect the privacy of every user. Unlike WhatsApp, exporting the conversation history in Kiki is not allowed."

"feedback_help_info_gone" : "Common Situations:

1. If you delete the Kiki app, all of your information will be deleted as well. Kiki does not save your personal information in their servers. Reinstalling the app will not bring back your information.

2. If you log in to Kiki on a new device, you will not be able to get your information because it was saved on the previous device.

3. If you have set up decoy passwords, make sure you enter the right one. Please note, each password has a separate private space.

4. If a Kiki friend deletes you from his/her Kiki friend list, all messages and media you received from this friend will also be deleted.

If you think your case is not one of these, please contact us."

"feedback_help_no_notification_alert" : "Please check the following settings:

1. Go to your device's "Settings" => "Application manager" or "Apps", find Kiki and tap it. Enable "Show notifications" in the app info screen.

2. Go to the "More"=>"Notification Setting" menu in Kiki and turn off "Do Not Disturb".

3. Go to the "Personalized Notifications" menu and make sure Notification Alerts is not turned off."

"invite_email_content" : "Hi, check out Kiki, the ultimate secure messaging app that allows you to make secure phone calls and send self-destructing messages for free.

Kiki gives you full control over messages you send. You can remotely wipe or recall messages – even add a self-destruct mechanism so they can't be passed around!

Kiki also provides an impenetrable vault for protecting your personal contacts, call logs, messages, confidential document, notes, diary and sensitive photos & videos from prying eyes.

Everything is stored and transmitted using unbreakable military-grade encryption - without the access code, no-one on the planet can access your data! Even if you lose your device or leave your device unattended – your data will never be revealed!

It's all free. So go get Kiki right now from http://sentryapp.me/a?p=%s"

"tips_tricks_auto_lock_in_background_detail" : "Kiki will lock two minutes after it is closed. This is a balance between security and convenience. If you want Kiki to lock immediately after it is closed, please
turn on"Auto Lock in Background"."

"tips_tricks_block_unwanted_call_detail" : "If you do not want certain people to reach you via your Kiki phone number(s), you can set up a whitelist and a blacklist. Any phone numbers on the blacklist will be blocked while those on the whitelist will be able to reach you.
Calls from numbers that are neither on the whitelist nor the blacklist will be sent to voicemail.
Block unwanted calls NOW."

"tips_tricks_delete_coverme_friend_detail" : "If you are done with a Kiki friend, simply delete the friend from your Kiki friend list. Both sides of the entire communication history will be completely erased."

"tips_tricks_do_not_disturb_details" : "You may not want your Kiki contacts to be able to reach you during a certain time, say 6:00 PM to 8:00 AM. This feature silences all incoming calls and texts during the time set.
Set up Do Not Disturb NOW."

"tips_tricks_dot_lock_for_coverme_vault_detail" : "You can set up a dot lock to add an additional layer of protection for your Kiki vault.
Set up Dot Lock for Kiki Vault NOW."
"tips_tricks_goto_dot_lock_for_coverme_vault" : "Set up Dot Lock for Kiki Vault NOW."

"tips_tricks_hide_login_screen_detail" : "You may not want the login screen to appear when someone opens the Kiki app. This feature keeps the login screen hidden until you tap three times.
Set up NOW."

"tips_tricks_hide_online_status_detail" : "When you are using Kiki, your Kiki friends can see that you are online. If you do not want your status known to all your Kiki friends, make your status as offline even when you are online.
Hide your online status NOW."

"tips_tricks_hide_register_phone_number_detail" : "If a person who has your phone number in his/her address book also installs Kiki, they will be able to see that you are on Kiki. If you do not want anyone to know that you are on Kiki, enable "Hide Your Registered Phone Number"."

"tips_tricks_intrusion_detection_detail" : "When someone (including you) tries to log in to Kiki with the wrong password, Kiki will take a picture from the front camera and record the location. You can view the intruder login history here.
You can also enter an Email address to receive intrusion alarms. This is a very useful feature if you lose your phone or leave it unattended.
Set up Email Alarm NOW."

"tips_tricks_notice" : "We work very hard to build lots of amazing features in to Kiki. Some of them are like pearls in deep, hidden places.
The following tips and tricks will help you get the most juice from Kiki."

"tips_tricks_remote_erase_message_detail" : "You can always recall messages you have sent no matter if they have been read or not. Simply tap the message and choose "Recall".
If you want to erase all the messages you have sent to a contact, simply swipe on the last message in the "Messages" screen and choose "Delete".
If you delete a contact from your Kiki friend list, all messages you have sent to this contact will be recalled. Leave no trace!"

"tips_tricks_self_destruct_message_detail" : "Messages sent from Kiki to non-Kiki users cannot be set to self-destruct. Please invite your contacts to use the Kiki app so that calling and texting will be more secure…and free!"

"tips_tricks_setup_customized_open_screen_detail" : "When you open Kiki, you will see three pictures on the lock screen. You can replace them with any pictures you want. You can even set the lock screen to shuffle through an entire album.
Set up NOW."

"tips_tricks_setup_personalized_notification_detail" : "When someone sends you a message, your device will display an alert similar to: "Your friend (ID 12345678) sent you a message". You may want the alert to be more discreet so Kiki allows you to create a customized notification.
Set up Customized Notification Alerts NOW."

"tips_tricks_use_decoy_password_detail" : "With this feature, you can set up multiple passwords in Kiki. Each password represents a totally separate account so your content and Kiki friends under one password will not be visible under another password.
Set up Decoy Password NOW."

"tips_tricks_use_strong_password_detail" : "Initially, you are required to use an all-number password that may not be strong enough. Enable Strong Password in order to use any combination of letters and numbers to create a much more secure password."

"feedback_help_calling_plan" : "1. Chaque forfait téléphonique a une date d'expiration. Veuillez renouveler ou réapprovisionner votre forfait téléphonique avant qu'il n'expire.

2. Si votre forfait téléphonique a déjà expiré, cela signifie que vous avez également perdu votre numéro de téléphone Kiki. Nous ne pouvons pas vous venir en aide concernant ce problème.

3. Dans de rares cas, le numéro de téléphone que vous avez choisi juste avant de souscrire le forfait téléphonique, peut devenir indisponible. Ne vous inquiétez pas, nous ne nous enfuirons pas avec votre argent. Vous pouvez choisir un autre numéro de téléphone pour le forfait téléphonique déjà souscrit.

4. Nous ne renouvelons pas automatiquement votre forfait téléphonique. Il n'y a pas de frais récurrents.

Si les réponses ci-dessus ne répondent pas à votre question, veuillez nous contacter."

"feedback_help_export_conversation_history" : "L'application Kiki est conçue pour protéger la vie privée de chaque utilisateur. Contrairement à WhatsApp, l'exportation de l'historique de la conversation dans Kiki n'est pas autorisée."

"feedback_help_info_gone" : "Situations courantes : 

1. Si vous supprimez l'application Kiki, toutes vos données seront également supprimées. Kiki n'enregistre pas vos données personnelles sur ses serveurs. La réinstallation de l'application ne vous permettra pas de récupérer vos données.

2. Si vous vous connectez à Kiki sur un nouvel appareil, vous ne pourrez pas accéder à vos données même si vous les aviez enregistrées sur l'ancien appareil.

3. Si vous avez configuré des mots de passe de type leurre, assurez-vous de bien saisir le mot de passe correct. Veuillez noter que chaque mot de passe permet d'accéder à un espace privé distinct.

4. Si un ami Kiki vous supprime de sa liste d'amis Kiki, tous les messages et documents reçus de cet ami seront également supprimés.

Si vous pensez que votre cas ne correspond pas à l'une de ces situations, veuillez nous contacter."

"feedback_help_no_notification_alert" : "Veuillez vérifier les paramètres suivants : 

1. Accédez au menu "Réglages"=>"Notifications", trouvez l'application Kiki et activez la notification pour Kiki.

2. Accédez au menu "Plus"=>"Paramètres de notification" dans Kiki et désactivez "Ne pas déranger".

3. Accédez au menu "Notifications personnalisées" et assurez-vous que les alertes de notification ne sont pas désactivées."
"feedback_help_notice" : "Si ces opérations ne permettent pas de résoudre votre problème, appuyez-ci-dessous."

"feedback_help_payment" : "Il faut parfois 3 à 5 jours ouvrés pour terminer certaines transactions PayPal.

Si vous voyez toujours la transaction en attente après 5 jours, veuillez nous contacter en nous fournissant votre reçu PayPal."

"feedback_help_personalized_notification" : "Vous pouvez configurer des alertes personnalisées pour toute notification provenant de vos cercles ou amis Kiki, ou pour les appels et SMS reçus sur vos numéros de téléphone Kiki.

Par exemple, vous pouvez remplacer "xxx vous a envoyé un message" par "Flash d'informations CNN".

Définir des notifications personnalisées maintenant."

"feedback_help_save_message_photo_video" : "L'application Kiki est conçue pour protéger la vie privée de chaque utilisateur. Par défaut, l'enregistrement des messages et des documents reçus n'est pas autorisé.

Si vous souhaitez enregistrer les messages et les documents que vous recevez, invitez l'expéditeur à sélectionner le niveau "Normal" pour le paramètre de sécurité de la messagerie avant d'effectuer l'envoi.

Remarque : Le paramètre de sécurité de votre messagerie ne vous permet pas de contrôler l'enregistrement des messages et des documents que vous recevez."

"hiddenmode_attention" : "Remarque :

1. Après avoir activé le mode Camouflage dans le menu "Paramètres de sécurité" de Kiki, l'icône Kiki disparaîtra. Si vous n'utilisez pas un système d'exploitation Android natif, vous devrez peut-être supprimer l'icône Kiki manuellement.

2. Saisissez le code ##PIN (par exemple ##1234) sur le clavier téléphonique, puis appuyez sur APPEL pour démarrer Kiki.

3. Au cas où vous n'arriveriez pas à démarrer Kiki depuis le clavier téléphonique, accédez au menu Paramètres -> Gestionnaire d'applications -> Kiki de votre appareil, puis appuyez sur "Gérer l'espace", et trouvez Kiki."

"invite_email_content" : "Bonjour, découvrez Kiki, l'ultime application de messagerie sécurisée qui vous permet de passer des appels téléphoniques sécurisés et d'envoyer des messages à autodestruction gratuitement.

Kiki vous offre un contrôle total sur les messages que vous envoyez. Vous pouvez effacer ou rappeler les messages à distance, et même ajouter un mécanisme d'autodestruction afin d'éviter leur propagation !

Kiki est également dotée d'un coffre-fort inviolable pour garder vos contacts personnels, journaux d'appels, messages, documents confidentiels, notes, agenda ainsi que vos photos et vidéos très privées à l'abri des regards indiscrets.

Tout est stocké et transmis à l'aide d'une technologie cryptographique de niveau militaire. Sans le code d'accès, personne sur la planète ne pourra accéder aux données ! Même si vous perdez votre appareil ou le laissez sans surveillance, vos données ne seront jamais dévoilées !

L'application est totalement gratuite. Alors téléchargez Kiki dès maintenant depuis http://sentryapp.me/a?p=%s"

"invite_friend_share_text" : "Essayez Kiki, une application de messagerie sécurisée et dotée d'un coffre-fort privé pour stocker vos photos, vidéos et contacts secrets. Téléchargez l'application depuis http://sentryapp.me/a?p=%s"

"share_unsecured_sharing_wechat_pic_content" : "Contrairement à Kiki, l'application WeChat ne permet pas de recevoir des photos protégées par chiffrement et vous ne pouvez pas rappeler les photos envoyées.

"share_unsecured_sharing_whatsapp_video_content" : "Contrairement à Kiki, l'application WhatsApp ne permet pas de recevoir des vidéos protégées par chiffrement et vous ne pouvez pas rappeler les vidéos envoyées.

"signin_activity_warning_text_please" : "Veuillez saisir le mot de passe correct après %s secondes."

"sina_share" : "Essayez Kiki, une application de messagerie sécurisée dotée d'un coffre-fort privé pour stocker vos contacts, photos et vidéos confidentiels. Téléchargez l'application à l'adresse suivante : http://sentryapp.me/d"
"strict_membership_content" : "L'adhésion sur invitation seulement est limitée à 100 membres."

"system_killed_coverme_dialog_content" : "Kiki semble avoir été arrêtée par le système Android ou un gestionnaire d'applications tiers. Kiki doit continuer à fonctionner en arrière-plan pour recevoir les appels et les SMS entrants.
Veuillez vous assurer que Kiki continue de fonctionner en arrière-plan."

"tips_tricks_auto_lock_in_background_detail" : "Kiki se verrouillera deux minutes après avoir quitté l'application. Ce laps de temps correspond à un équilibre entre sécurité et commodité. Si vous voulez que Kiki se verrouille immédiatement après avoir quitté l'application, veuillez
activer "Verrouillage automatique en arrière-plan"."

"tips_tricks_block_unwanted_call_detail" : "Si vous ne voulez pas que certaines personnes puissent vous joindre via votre ou vos numéros de téléphone Kiki, vous pouvez définir une liste blanche et une liste noire. Les numéros de téléphone figurant sur la liste noire seront bloqués alors que ceux de la liste blanche pourront vous joindre.
Les appels provenant de numéros figurant ni sur la liste blanche, ni sur la liste noire seront dirigés vers la messagerie vocale.
Bloquer les appels indésirables MAINTENANT."
"tips_tricks_coverme_vs_no_coverme" : "Communication avec les utilisateurs Kiki et non Kiki"

"tips_tricks_delete_coverme_friend_detail" : "Si vous ne souhaitez plus être ami avec un utilisateur de Kiki, il suffit de le supprimer de votre liste d'amis Kiki. L'intégralité de l'historique de la communication sera effacée pour les deux utilisateurs."

"tips_tricks_do_not_disturb_details" : "Vous souhaiterez peut-être vous rendre indisponible de telle sorte que vos contacts Kiki ne puissent pas vous joindre pendant un certain temps, par exemple de 18 h 00 à 08 h 00. Cette fonctionnalité permet de passer en mode silencieux pour les appels et les SMS entrants sur la période prédéfinie.
Configurer "Ne pas déranger" MAINTENANT."
"tips_tricks_dot_lock_for_coverme_vault" : "Schéma de verrouillage pour le coffre-fort Kiki"

"tips_tricks_dot_lock_for_coverme_vault_detail" : "Vous pouvez définir un schéma de verrouillage pour ajouter un dispositif de protection supplémentaire à votre coffre-fort Kiki.
Définir un schéma de verrouillage pour le coffre-fort Kiki MAINTENANT."
"tips_tricks_goto_dot_lock_for_coverme_vault" : "Définir un schéma de verrouillage pour le coffre-fort Kiki MAINTENANT."
"tips_tricks_goto_setup_personalized_notification" : "Définir des alertes de notification personnalisées MAINTENANT."
"tips_tricks_goto_use_decoy_password" : "Définir un mot de passe leurre MAINTENANT."
"tips_tricks_goto_use_strong_password" : "Activez la fonctionnalité Mot de passe fort"

"tips_tricks_hide_login_screen_detail" : "Vous souhaiterez peut-être que l'écran de connexion ne s'affiche pas si quelqu'un ouvre l'application Kiki. Cette fonctionnalité masque l'écran de connexion jusqu'à ce que vous appuyiez trois fois dessus. 
Configurer MAINTENANT."

"tips_tricks_hide_online_status_detail" : "Lorsque vous utilisez Kiki, vos amis Kiki peuvent voir que vous êtes en ligne. Si vous voulez rendre votre statut en ligne invisible auprès de tous vos amis Kiki, paramétrez votre statut afin qu'il affiche hors ligne même si vous êtes en ligne.
Masquer votre statut en ligne MAINTENANT."

"tips_tricks_hide_register_phone_number_detail" : "Si une personne qui a votre numéro de téléphone dans son carnet d'adresses installe également Kiki, elle pourra voir que vous êtes un utilisateur de Kiki. Si vous ne voulez pas que tout le monde sache que vous êtes un utilisateur de Kiki, activez l'option "Masquer votre numéro de téléphone enregistré"."

"tips_tricks_intrusion_detection_detail" : "Lorsque quelqu'un (vous y compris) essaie d'ouvrir une session Kiki avec un mot de passe incorrect, Kiki prend une photo avec le capteur situé sur la face avant de l'appareil et enregistre le lieu de la tentative d'intrusion. Vous pouvez afficher l'historique des connexions intrusives ici.
Vous pouvez également saisir une adresse e-mail pour recevoir des alarmes d'intrusion. C'est une fonctionnalité très utile si vous perdez votre téléphone ou le laisser sans surveillance.
Définir une alarme par e-mail MAINTENANT."

"tips_tricks_notice" : "Nous travaillons sans relâche pour développer de remarquables fonctionnalités dans Kiki. Certaines d'entre elles sont comme des perles cachées dans les profondeurs.
Les conseils et astuces ci-dessous vous aideront à découvrir le meilleur de Kiki."

"tips_tricks_remote_erase_message_detail" : "Vous pouvez toujours rappeler les messages que vous avez envoyés, qu'ils aient été lus ou non. Appuyez simplement sur le message et choisissez "Rappeler".
Si vous voulez effacer tous les messages envoyés à un contact, accédez à l'écran "Messages", faites glisser jusqu'au dernier message et choisissez "Supprimer".
Si vous supprimez un contact de votre liste d'amis Kiki, tous les messages que vous avez envoyés à ce contact seront rappelés. Ne laissez aucune trace !"

"tips_tricks_self_destruct_message_detail" : "Les messages envoyés par des utilisateurs Kiki à des utilisateurs n'utilisant pas Kiki ne peuvent pas bénéficier de l'option d'autodestruction. Veuillez inviter vos contacts à utiliser l'application Kiki afin que vos appels et vos SMS soient sécurisés....et gratuits !"

"tips_tricks_setup_customized_open_screen_detail" : "Lorsque vous ouvrez Kiki, trois images s'affichent sur l'écran de verrouillage. Vous pouvez les remplacer par des images de votre choix. Vous pouvez même régler l'écran de verrouillage de telle sorte que des images soient choisies de manière aléatoire dans un album entier. 
Configurer MAINTENANT."

"tips_tricks_setup_personalized_notification_detail" : "Lorsque quelqu'un vous envoie un message, votre appareil affichera une alerte similaire à: "Votre ami (ID 12345678) vous a envoyé un message". Vous souhaiterez peut-être rendre cette alerte plus discrète. Ainsi, Kiki vous permet de créer une notification personnalisée.
Définir des alertes de notification personnalisées MAINTENANT."

"tips_tricks_use_decoy_password_detail" : "Avec cette fonctionnalité, vous pouvez configurer plusieurs mots de passe dans Kiki. Chaque mot de passe donne accès à un compte totalement distinct si bien que le contenu et les amis Kiki correspondant à un mot de passe ne seront pas visibles si vous utilisez un autre mot de passe. 
Définir un mot de passe leurre MAINTENANT."

"tips_tricks_use_strong_password_detail" : "Au départ, vous êtes tenu d'utiliser un mot de passe composé uniquement de chiffres, susceptible de ne pas être suffisamment fort. Activez la fonctionnalité Mot de passe fort afin d'utiliser une combinaison aléatoire de lettres et de chiffres et créer un mot de passe beaucoup plus sécurisé."

"feedback_help_calling_plan" : "1. Arama tarifelerinin her birinin son kullanım tarihi vardır. Lütfen son kullanma süresi dolmadan arama tarifenizi yenileyin ya da yeniden doldurun.

2. Arama tarifeniz zaten dolduysa, Kiki telefon numaranızı da kaybetmişsinizdir. Bu sorunla ilgili size yardımcı olamayız.

3. Nadiren karşılaşılan durumlarda, arama tarifesi satın almadan önce seçtiğiniz telefon numarası kullanım dışı kalabilir. Endişelenmeyin, paranızı alıp kaçamyız. Halihazırda satın aldığınız arama tarifesi için başka bir telefon numarası seçebilirsiniz.

4. Arama tarifenizi otomatik olarak yenilemeyiz. Tekrar eden ödeme yoktur.

Yukarıdaki cevaplar sorunuza karşılık gelmiyorsa, lütfen bizimle iletişime geçin."
"feedback_help_export_conversation_history" : "Kiki her kullanıcının gizliliğini korumak için tasarlanmıştır. WhatsApp'tan farklı olarak, Kiki'deki sohbet geçmişini dışa aktarmaya izin verilmez."

"feedback_help_info_gone" : "Ortak Durumlar:

1. Kiki uygulamasını silerseniz, tüm bilgileriniz de silinecektir. Kiki kişisel bilgilerinizi sunucularına kaydetmez. Uygulamayı yeniden yüklemek bilgilerinizi geri getirmeyecektir.

2. Kiki'ye yeni bir cihazdan giriş yaparsanız, bilgilerinizi alamayabilirsiniz, çünkü bu bilgiler bir önceki cihaza kaydedilmiştir.

3. Sahte şifre kurduysanız, doğru olanı girdiğinizden emin olun. Lütfen her bir şifrenin ayrı özel bir alanı olduğunu unutmayın.

4. Kiki arkadaşınız sizi Kiki arkadaş listesinden silerse, bu arkadaştan aldığınız tüm mesajlar ve medya dosyaları da silinecektir.

Eğer sorununuzun bunlardan birisi olduğunu düşünmüyorsanız, lütfen bizimle iletişime geçin."

"feedback_help_no_notification_alert" : "Lütfen aşağıdaki ayarları kontrol edin:

1. Cihazınızın "Ayarlar" => "Bildirimler" menüsüne girin, Kiki'yi bulun ve Kiki için bildirimleri etkinleştirin.

2. Kiki'deki "Daha Fazlası" => "Bildirim Ayarı" menüsüne girin ve "Rahatsız Etme" bölümü kapatın.

3. "Kişiselleştirilmiş Bildirimler" menüsüne girin ve Bildirim Uyarılarının kapalı olmadığından emin olun."

1. Kiki'nin "Güvenlik Ayarları" menüsünden Kılık Değiştirme Modunu etkinleştirdiğinizde, normal Kiki ikonu yok olacaktır. Doğal Android bir işletim sistemi kullanmıyorsanız, Kiki ikonunu kendiniz silmeniz gerekecektir.

"invite_email_content" : "Selamlar, ücretsiz olarak güvenli telefon aramaları yapmanıza ve kendi kendini yok eden mesajlar göndermenize izin veren, en son ve en yüksek güvenlilikli mesajlaşma uygulaması olan Kiki'ye göz atın.

Kiki, gönderdiğiniz mesajlarda size tam kontrol verir. Mesajları uzaktan silebilir veya onları devreye sokabilirsiniz – hatta bu mesajların elden ele gezmemesi için kendi kendini yok eden mekanizma ekleyebilirsiniz!

Bunun yanında Kiki kişisel kontaklarınızı, arama kayıtlarınızı, mesajlarınızı, çok gizli dokümanlarınızı, notlarınızı, günlüğünüzü ve hassas fotoğraflarınızı ve videolarınızı meraklı gözlerden korumak için girilmesi imkansız bir kasa dairesi sunar.

Kırılamaz askeri giriş şifrelemesi kullanılarak herşey depolanır ve iletilir – giriş kodu olmadan gezegendeki hiç kimse verilerinize erişemez! Cihazınızı kaybetseniz veya onu kullanmayı bıraksanız bile – verileriniz asla ortaya çıkmayacak!

Tüm bunlar tamamen ücretsiz. Bu yüzden hemen şimdi http://sentryapp.me/a?p=%s adresinden Kiki edinin."

"feedback_help_calling_plan" : "1. Todos los planes de llamadas tienen una fecha de vencimiento. Renueva o recarga el plan de llamadas antes de que expire.

2. Si tu plan de llamadas expira, habrás perdido tu número de teléfono de Kiki. No podemos ayudarte con esto.

3. En raras ocasiones, el número de teléfono que has escogido justo antes de comprar el plan de llamadas puede dejar de estar disponible. No te preocupes, no saldremos corriendo con tu dinero. Puedes seleccionar otro número de teléfono para el plan de llamadas que comprado.

4. No renovamos automáticamente el plan de llamadas. No hay cargos recurrentes.

Si las respuestas anteriores no se aplican a tu pregunta, contáctanos."

"feedback_help_export_conversation_history" : "Kiki está diseñado para proteger la privacidad de todos los usuarios. A diferencia de WhatsApp, no se puede exportar el historial de conversaciones de Kiki."

"feedback_help_info_gone" : "Situaciones frecuentes:

1. Si eliminas la aplicación de Kiki, también se eliminará toda tu información. Kiki no guarda tu información personal en sus servidores. Reinstalar la aplicación no hará que la información se recupere.

2. Si accedes a Kiki desde un nuevo dispositivo, no dispondrás de tu información, ya que se habrá guardado en el dispositivo anterior.

3. Si has establecido contraseñas señuelo, asegúrate de introducir la correcta. Ten en cuenta que cada contraseña tiene un espacio privado distinto.

4. Si un amigo de Kiki te elimina de su lista de amigos de Kiki, los mensajes y contenidos recibidos de parte de este amigo, también se eliminarán.

"invite_email_content" : "Hola. Echa un vistazo a Kiki, la más novedosa aplicación de mensajería segura, que te permite hacer llamadas telefónicas seguras y enviar mensajes autodestructibles en forma gratuita.

Kiki te da un control total sobre los mensajes que envías. Puedes borrar o recuperar mensajes a distancia, ¡y hasta agregar un mecanismo de autodestrucción para que no circulen!

Kiki también brinda una bóveda impenetrable para proteger de las miradas indiscretas tus contactos personales, registros de llamadas, mensajes, documentos confidenciales, notas, diario, y fotos y videos sensibles.

Todo se almacena y transmite mediante un cifrado inviolable de nivel militar: sin el código de acceso, ¡nadie en el mundo puede acceder a tus datos! Incluso, si pierdes tu dispositivo o lo dejas sin vigilancia, ¡tu información nunca será revelada!

Todo gratis. Descarga Kiki ahora desde http://sentryapp.me/a?p=%s"

"tips_tricks_hide_login_screen_detail" : "Puede que no quieras que aparezca la pantalla de acceso cuando alguien abra Kiki. Esta característica mantiene oculta la pantalla de acceso hasta que toques tres veces.
Establecer ahora."

"tips_tricks_hide_online_status_detail" : "Cuando usas la app, tus amigos de Kiki pueden ver que estás en línea. Si no quieres que tu estado sea visible para todos tus amigos de Kiki, haz que diga "desconectado" incluso si estás conectado.
Esconde tu estado en línea ahora."

"tips_tricks_hide_register_phone_number_detail" : "Si una persona que tiene tu número en su libreta de direcciones también instala Kiki, podrá ver que estás en Kiki. Si no quieres que los demás sepan que usas Kiki, habilita "Ocultar número de teléfono registrado"."

"tips_tricks_intrusion_detection_detail" : "Cuando alguien (incluso tú) intente acceder a Kiki con una contraseña incorrecta, Kiki tomará una foto con la cámara frontal y registrará la ubicación. Puedes ver el historial de intrusiones aquí.
También puedes ingresar una dirección de email para recibir alarmas de intrusión. Esta es una función muy útil si pierdes el teléfono o lo dejas desatendido.
Establecer alarma por email AHORA."

"tips_tricks_notice" : "Trabajamos mucho para hacer montones de características geniales para Kiki. Algunas son como perlas ocultas en las profundidades.
Los siguientes consejos y trucos te ayudarán a sacarle todo el jugo a Kiki."

"tips_tricks_remote_erase_message_detail" : "Siempre puedes recuperar los mensajes enviados, independientemente de que se hayan leído o no. Tan sólo toca el mensaje y elige "Recuperar".
Si deseas borrar todos los mensajes enviados a un contacto, simplemente deslízate sobre el último mensaje en la pantalla "Mensajes" y selecciona "Eliminar".
Si eliminas a un contacto de tu lista de amigos de Kiki, se recuperarán todos los mensajes enviados a ese contacto. ¡No dejes rastro!"

"tips_tricks_self_destruct_message_detail" : "Los mensajes enviados desde Kiki hacia fuera de Kiki no se pueden autodestruir. Invita a tus contactos a usar Kiki que llamadas y textos san más seguros... ¡y gratis!"

"tips_tricks_setup_customized_open_screen_detail" : "Al abrir Kiki, verás tres imágenes en la pantalla de bloqueo. Puedes reemplazarlas con las imágenes que desees. Incluso puedes configurar la pantalla de bloqueo para que alterne con un álbum completo.
Configurar AHORA."

"tips_tricks_setup_personalized_notification_detail" : "Cuando alguien te envíe un mensaje, el dispositivo mostrará una alerta similar a: "Tu amigo (ID 12345678) te ha enviado un mensaje". Puede que desees que la alerta sea más discreta, por lo que Kiki te permite crear notificaciones personalizadas.
Establecer alertas de notificación personalizadas AHORA."

"tips_tricks_use_decoy_password_detail" : "Con esta función, puedes establecer múltiples contraseñas en Kiki. Cada contraseña representa una cuenta totalmente separada, por lo que el contenido y los amigos protegidos por una contraseña no serán visibles ingresando con otra.
Establecer contraseña señuelo AHORA."

"tips_tricks_use_strong_password_detail" : "Al principio se te pide que uses una contraseña numérica que puede no ser lo suficientemente fuerte. Habilita la Contraseña Fuerte para usar cualquier combinación de letras y números, y crear una contraseña mucho más segura."

"feedback_help_calling_plan" : "1. Cada plano de chamadas possui uma data de expiração. Por favor renove ou recarregue seu plano de chamadas antes que ele expire.

3. Em raras situações, o número de telefone escolhido no instante anterior à compra pode ter se tornado indisponível. Não se preocupe, nós não iremos fugir com seu dinheiro. Você pode selecionar outro número de telefone para o plano de chamadas já adquirido.

4. Nós não renovamos seu plano de chamadas automaticamente. Não há cobrança recorrente.

Se as respostas acima não solucionam sua dúvida, por favor entre em contato conosco."

"feedback_help_info_gone" : "Situações Comuns:

1. Se você excluir o aplicativo Kiki, todas as suas informações serão também excluídas. O Kiki não salva suas informações pessoais em seus servidores. Reinstalar o aplicativo não irá trazer suas informações de volta.

2. Se você fizer login no Kiki com um novo dispositivo, você não poderá recuperar suas informações porque elas terão sido salvas em um dispositivo anterior.

3. Se você definiu senhas de disfarce, certifique-se de utilizar a senha correta. Por favor note que cada senha possui um espaço privativo separado.

4. Se um amigo Kiki lhe excluir de sua lista de amigos Kiki, todas as mensagens e arquivos de mídia recebidos deste amigo também serão excluídos.

Se você acha que seu caso não é nenhum desses, por favor entre em contato conosco."

"invite_email_content" : "Olá, eu gostaria de lhe indicar o Kiki, o aplicativo definitivo para envio de mensagens com segurança que permite a realização de chamadas seguras e o envio de mensagens autodestrutivas gratuitas. 

 O Kiki lhe dá total controle sobre as mensagens enviadas. Você pode limpar ou recuperar mensagens remotamente - e até adicionar um mecanismo de autodestruição para evitar que essas mensagens sejam encaminhadas!

O Kiki também oferece um cofre impenetrável para a proteção de seus contatos pessoais, registros de chamada, mensagens, documentos confidenciais, notas, diário e fotos e vídeos privativos contra olhos curiosos.

Tudo é armazenado e transmitido utilizando criptografia inquebrável de nível militar - sem o código de acesso, ninguém no mundo pode acessar seus dados! Mesmo que seu dispositivo seja perdido ou esquecido seus dados jamais serão revelados!

E é tudo grátis. Então baixe o Kiki agora mesmo em http://sentryapp.me/a?p=%s"

"tips_tricks_block_unwanted_call_detail" : "Se você deseja que certas pessoas não possam lhe contactar pelo número de telefone Kiki, você pode definir uma lista branca e uma lista negra. "tips_tricks_delete_coverme_friend_detail" : "Se você não deseja mais manter um amigo Kiki, simplesmente exclua o amigo de sua lista de amigos. Ambos os lados de todo o histórico de comunicação serão totalmente apagados."

"tips_tricks_do_not_disturb_details" : "Você pode desejar que seus contatos do Kiki não possam lhe contactar durante um determinado período, por exemplo, entre 6 e 8 da manhã. Esta funcionalidade silencia todas as chamadas e mensagens recebidas durante o intervalo definido.

Configurar AGORA."

"tips_tricks_hide_online_status_detail" : "Quando você está usando o Kiki, seus amigos Kiki podem ver que você está online. Se você não deseja que seu status seja visível a todos os seus amigos, deixe-o como offline mesmo quando estiver disponível.

"tips_tricks_intrusion_detection_detail" : "Quando alguém (incluindo você mesmo) tente fazer login no Kiki com uma senha incorreta, o Kiki irá tirar uma foto pela câmera frontal e registrar a localização. Você pode ver o histórico de logins intrusos aqui.
Você também pode definir um endereço de Email para receber alertas de intrusão. Esta é uma funcionalidade muito útil para o caso de perda ou esquecimento do aparelho.
Configurar Alertas por Email AGORA."

"tips_tricks_notice" : "Nós trabalhamos arduamente para construir várias funcionalidades incríveis para o Kiki. Algumas delas são como tesouros escondidos.
As dicas e truques a seguir irão ajudá-lo a tirar o máximo proveito do Kiki."

"tips_tricks_remote_erase_message_detail" : "Você sempre pode recuperar mensagens enviadas, independentemente delas terem sido lidas ou não. Simplesmente toque na mensagem e escolha "Recuperar".
Se você deseja excluir todas as mensagens enviadas para um contato, simplesmente deslize na última mensagem na tela "Mensagens" e escolha "Excluir".
Se você excluir um contato de sua lista de amigos Kiki, todas as mensagens enviadas para este contato serão recuperadas. Não deixe vestígios!"

"tips_tricks_self_destruct_message_detail" : "Mensagens enviadas usuários Kiki para usuários não-Kiki não podem ser definidas para autodestruição. Por favor convide seus contatos a utilizar o Kiki para que chamadas e mensagens sejam mais seguras... e grátis!"

"tips_tricks_setup_customized_open_screen_detail" : "Quando abrir o Kiki, você verá três imagens na tela de bloqueio. Você pode substituí-las por qualquer imagem que desejar. Você pode até mesmo definir que a tela de bloqueio exiba uma imagem aleatória de um álbum inteiro.
Configurar AGORA."

"tips_tricks_setup_personalized_notification_detail" : "Quando alguém envia uma mensagem, seu dispositivo exibirá um alerta semelhante a : "Seu amigo (ID 12345678) enviou uma mensagem". Você pode desejar que o alerta seja mais discreto e, sendo assim, o Kiki permite que você crie uma notificação personalizada.
Configurar Alertas de Notificação Personalizados AGORA."

"tips_tricks_use_decoy_password_detail" : "Com esta funcionalidade, você pode definido múltiplas senhas no Kiki. Cada senha representa uma conta totalmente separada, de modo que seu conteúdo e amigos Kiki relacionados a uma senha não serão visíveis sob outra senha.
Configurar Senha de Disfarce AGORA."

"tips_tricks_use_strong_password_detail" : "Inicialmente, você deve utilizar uma senha numérica que pode não ser suficientemente forte. Ative a Senha Forte para utilizar qualquer combinação de letras e números para criar uma senha muito mais segura."

"feedback_help_info_gone" : "常见情况：

1：如果您删除Kiki，您的所有资料将被一同删除，Kiki的资料是保存在您的手机内而不是保存在我们的服务器上的，重装无法找回被删除的资料。

2：如果您在一个新设备上登录了Kiki，无法取回您的在上一台设备上的资料，您的资料依然在原有的设备上。

3：如果您设置了别的密码，每个密码都有独立的私密空间，确认您登录的是您想要登录的密码。

4：如果您的Kiki好友把您删除了，您从这个好友那里收到的所有消息和文件也将消失。

如果您遇到的不是上述情况，请与我们联系。"

"invite_email_content" : "你好, Kiki是一个智能手机上的应用。简单地讲，Kiki是私密微信+私密保险箱。你把Kiki下载到手机上，把最重要、最私密的联系人信息、短信、文档、笔记、日记、照片、视频用Kiki来加密保存。从此只有你自己才能看到这些私密信息。即使你把手机丢了，没有人能够从技术上解密这些私密信息。

"feedback_help_calling_plan" : "1. Each calling package has an expiration date. Please renew or refill the calling package before it expires.

2. If your calling package has already expired, you have also lost your Kiki phone number. We cannot help you on this issue.

3. In rare situations, the phone number you chose right before purchasing the calling package may become unavailable. Don't worry, we don't just grab your money and run. You can select another phone number for the calling package you already purchased.

4. We do not automatically renew your calling package. There is no recurring charge.

If the above answers do not address your question, please contact us."

"feedback_help_coverme_phone_number" : "2. We only provide U.S. and Canadian phone numbers at this time and you can only make calls and send texts to U.S., Canadian, and Chinese phone numbers. However, you can receive calls and texts from any phone number anywhere in the world.

U.K. phone numbers coming soon!

3. A Kiki phone number is always attached to a calling package you have purchased. If the calling package expires, you permanently lose the phone number. Please make sure you renew your calling package before it expires.

4. You can get up to 10 Kiki phone numbers simultaneously.

5. We always recommend that you invite your contacts to use the Kiki app too. Calling and texting between Kiki users is more secure and is always free.

If the above answers do not address your question, please contact us."
"feedback_help_export_conversation_history" : "Kiki is designed to protect the privacy of every user. Unlike WhatsApp, exporting the conversation history in Kiki is not allowed."

"feedback_help_info_gone" : "Common Situations:

1. If you delete the Kiki app, all of your information will be deleted as well. Kiki does not save your personal information in their servers. Reinstalling the app will not bring back your information.

2. If you log in to Kiki on a new device, you will not be able to get your information because it was saved on the previous device.

3. If you have set up decoy passwords, make sure you enter the right one. Please note, each password has a separate private space.

4. If a Kiki friend deletes you from his/her Kiki friend list, all messages and media you received from this friend will also be deleted.

If you think your case is not one of these, please contact us."

"feedback_help_no_notification_alert" : "Please check the following settings:

1. Go to your device's "Settings" => "Application manager" or "Apps", find Kiki and tap it. Enable "Show notifications" in the app info screen.

2. Go to the "More"=>"Notification Setting" menu in Kiki and turn off "Do Not Disturb".

3. Go to the "Personalized Notifications" menu and make sure Notification Alerts is not turned off."

"invite_email_content" : "Hi, check out Kiki, the ultimate secure messaging app that allows you to make secure phone calls and send self-destructing messages for free.

Kiki gives you full control over messages you send. You can remotely wipe or recall messages – even add a self-destruct mechanism so they can't be passed around!

Kiki also provides an impenetrable vault for protecting your personal contacts, call logs, messages, confidential document, notes, diary and sensitive photos & videos from prying eyes.

Everything is stored and transmitted using unbreakable military-grade encryption - without the access code, no-one on the planet can access your data! Even if you lose your device or leave your device unattended – your data will never be revealed!

It's all free. So go get Kiki right now from http://sentryapp.me/a?p=%s"

"tips_tricks_auto_lock_in_background_detail" : "Kiki will lock two minutes after it is closed. This is a balance between security and convenience. If you want Kiki to lock immediately after it is closed, please
turn on"Auto Lock in Background"."

"tips_tricks_block_unwanted_call_detail" : "If you do not want certain people to reach you via your Kiki phone number(s), you can set up a whitelist and a blacklist. Any phone numbers on the blacklist will be blocked while those on the whitelist will be able to reach you.
Calls from numbers that are neither on the whitelist nor the blacklist will be sent to voicemail.
Block unwanted calls NOW."

"tips_tricks_delete_coverme_friend_detail" : "If you are done with a Kiki friend, simply delete the friend from your Kiki friend list. Both sides of the entire communication history will be completely erased."

"tips_tricks_do_not_disturb_details" : "You may not want your Kiki contacts to be able to reach you during a certain time, say 6:00 PM to 8:00 AM. This feature silences all incoming calls and texts during the time set.
Set up Do Not Disturb NOW."

"tips_tricks_dot_lock_for_coverme_vault_detail" : "You can set up a dot lock to add an additional layer of protection for your Kiki vault.
Set up Dot Lock for Kiki Vault NOW."
"tips_tricks_goto_dot_lock_for_coverme_vault" : "Set up Dot Lock for Kiki Vault NOW."

"tips_tricks_hide_login_screen_detail" : "You may not want the login screen to appear when someone opens the Kiki app. This feature keeps the login screen hidden until you tap three times.
Set up NOW."

"tips_tricks_hide_online_status_detail" : "When you are using Kiki, your Kiki friends can see that you are online. If you do not want your status known to all your Kiki friends, make your status as offline even when you are online.
Hide your online status NOW."

"tips_tricks_hide_register_phone_number_detail" : "If a person who has your phone number in his/her address book also installs Kiki, they will be able to see that you are on Kiki. If you do not want anyone to know that you are on Kiki, enable "Hide Your Registered Phone Number"."

"tips_tricks_intrusion_detection_detail" : "When someone (including you) tries to log in to Kiki with the wrong password, Kiki will take a picture from the front camera and record the location. You can view the intruder login history here.
You can also enter an Email address to receive intrusion alarms. This is a very useful feature if you lose your phone or leave it unattended.
Set up Email Alarm NOW."

"tips_tricks_notice" : "We work very hard to build lots of amazing features in to Kiki. Some of them are like pearls in deep, hidden places.
The following tips and tricks will help you get the most juice from Kiki."

"tips_tricks_remote_erase_message_detail" : "You can always recall messages you have sent no matter if they have been read or not. Simply tap the message and choose "Recall".
If you want to erase all the messages you have sent to a contact, simply swipe on the last message in the "Messages" screen and choose "Delete".
If you delete a contact from your Kiki friend list, all messages you have sent to this contact will be recalled. Leave no trace!"

"tips_tricks_self_destruct_message_detail" : "Messages sent from Kiki to non-Kiki users cannot be set to self-destruct. Please invite your contacts to use the Kiki app so that calling and texting will be more secure…and free!"

"tips_tricks_setup_customized_open_screen_detail" : "When you open Kiki, you will see three pictures on the lock screen. You can replace them with any pictures you want. You can even set the lock screen to shuffle through an entire album.
Set up NOW."

"tips_tricks_setup_personalized_notification_detail" : "When someone sends you a message, your device will display an alert similar to: "Your friend (ID 12345678) sent you a message". You may want the alert to be more discreet so Kiki allows you to create a customized notification.
Set up Customized Notification Alerts NOW."

"tips_tricks_use_decoy_password_detail" : "With this feature, you can set up multiple passwords in Kiki. Each password represents a totally separate account so your content and Kiki friends under one password will not be visible under another password.
Set up Decoy Password NOW."

"tips_tricks_use_strong_password_detail" : "Initially, you are required to use an all-number password that may not be strong enough. Enable Strong Password in order to use any combination of letters and numbers to create a much more secure password."
"tips_tricks_why_need_a_coverme_phone_number" : "Why Do I Need Kiki Phone Numbers?"

"feedback_explain" : "請詳細描述您的建議或您遇到的問題："

"feedback_help_calling_plan" : "1：每個通話套餐都有一個有效期，過期後需要續費才能繼續使用。

2：Kiki私密號碼是和通話套餐關聯的，如果套餐過期了您的號碼將會被回收。

3：極少數情況下您的私密號碼會在套餐過期之前被回收，不過不用擔心，我們會免費讓您再選一個新號碼。

4：您需要手動續費，我們不支持自動續費。

如果以上答案不能解決您的問題，請與我們聯系。"

"feedback_help_coverme_phone_number" : "2：我們暫時只提供美國和加拿大的電話號碼，您只能給美國、加拿大和中國的號碼打電話和發短信。但是您可以收到來自世界上任何一個電話號碼的來電和短信。
英國的電話號碼即將推出，請繼續關注。

3：Kiki私密號碼是和通話套餐關聯的，如果套餐過期了您的號碼將會被回收，請及時續費。

4：您最多可以同時擁有10個Kiki私密號碼（十卡十待）。

5：我們始終建議您邀請您的聯系人安裝Kiki，Kiki用戶之間的聊天更安全方便，而且永久免費。

如果以上答案不能解決您的問題，請與我們聯系。"
"feedback_help_export_conversation_history" : "不像微信等自由開放的聊天App，Kiki的宗旨是保護每個用戶的隱私，因此不允許導出聊天記錄。"

"feedback_help_info_gone" : "常見情況：

1：如果您刪除Kiki，您的所有資料將被一同刪除，Kiki的資料是保存在您的手機內而不是保存在我們的服務器上的，重裝無法找回被刪除的資料。

2：如果您在一個新設備上登錄了Kiki，無法取回您的在上一台設備上的資料，您的資料依然在原有的設備上。

3：如果您設置了別的密碼，每個密碼都有獨立的私密空間，確認您登錄的是您想要登錄的密碼。

4：如果您的Kiki好友把您刪除了，您從這個好友那裏收到的所有消息和文件也將消失。

如果您遇到的不是上述情況，請與我們聯系。"

"hiddenmode_attention" : "注意：

1、開啓隱藏模式後，Kiki圖標將從桌面上刪除。

"invite_email_content" : "你好, Kiki是一個智能手機上的應用。簡單地講，Kiki是私密微信+私密保險箱。你把Kiki下載到手機上，把最重要、最私密的聯系人信息、短信、文檔、筆記、日記、照片、視頻用Kiki來加密保存。從此只有你自己才能看到這些私密信息。即使你把手機丟了，沒有人能夠從技術上解密這些私密信息。

你還可以用Kiki打加密電話，發送加密短信。任何人無法竊聽，偷窺你的短信與通話記錄。即使到營業廳打印出來的話單也沒有使用Kiki的通話記錄。

最棒的是，你用Kiki發送給別人的短信，照片，會自動銷毀掉。徹底杜絕豔照門的發生！

快快給你的手機下載Kiki吧， http://sentryapp.me/a?p=%s"

"tips_tricks_do_not_disturb_details" : "您可能不希望您的Kiki好友在您的休息時間聯系您，比如您設置勿擾時間段爲下午6點到早上8點，所有來電和短信都將在這段時間內靜音。

playstore_details.title: Kiki Chat Messenger: Free Private Friends Chats
playstore_details.description:
Kiki Chat Messenger --- Instant, private, secure!

Kiki Chat Messenger is a free & private instant messaging app tailored for Android devices. It helps you enjoy instant messaging in a safe and secure way, connect with anyone constantly wherever you go! 

With Kiki, you can securely send and receive instant text messages, make private phone calls, share photos, videos, emojis, stickers, audio, documents and many more, and explore a growing set of new features that help you stay connected. 

Why Choose Kiki Chat Messenger?
• Free Instant Messaging
Kiki Chat Messenger makes connecting easier! Simply choose a friend from your contacts, invite him or her to Kiki, and you are free to chat, call and share with each other. 

• Private Friends Chats
Thanks to our end-to-end encryption, any type of information you share on Kiki Chat Messenger will always remain to yourself and the person you’re talking to. Keep yourself away from prying eyes.

• Express Yourself with Emojis and Stickers
There are so much that words cannot say, but emojis and stickers can do! Express your moments or emotion with fun emojis and stickers in Kiki Chat Messenger. 

• Create Groups for Privacy
Wanna catch up with friends, family or business partners in a safe and private way? Just create a circle and invite them to it. Never worry about the privacy issues that are common on other social media networks, or your confidential business information being spread, intercepted, or hacked. Your privacy is 100% safe with Kiki Chat Messenger. 

• Secure Sharing
Sharing is everywhere. Whenever you need a share for work, or for private, Kiki is right here! With Kiki Chat Messenger, all your shares including photos, videos, audio, documents, locations, contacts are well protected with our security system. 

• Self-Destructing Secret Chats
Start a secret chat by setting up a self-destruct timer for your conversations. All messages you sent will be automatically deleted from both your and the recipient’s phones once the message is read. 

• Low-Cost Calls to Mobile and Landlines 
To call mobile or landlines, you don’t need Wi-Fi or cellular data but the Kiki Chat Messenger. Kiki allows you to call any mobile and landlines around the world with its low-cost international calling services. It can save a bundle off your current phone bills!

• And So Much More:
√ Shake your phone to lock the screen 
√ Personalize notifications to disguise incoming messages
√ Set fake passwords for others while you know the real one
√ Store photos, videos, documents, passwords to Kiki vault
√ Private phone calls with no records on phone bills
√ Block unwanted calls or spam calls
√ Customize your own voicemail greetings

Install Kiki Chat Messenger and Start Connecting Now!
